description: The clock is ticking to avoid the worst effects of a climate disaster, but I am optimistic about the ingenuity of people and the power of innovation: https://gatesnot.es/3pW0f2N #COP26
In addition to investments in reducing emissions to slow climate change, we need to help those already impacted by climate change adapt.
At this year’s UN Climate Conference #COP26, I’ll be talking about why I’m optimistic about our progress on climate change and the critical role that innovation will play:
To avoid a climate disaster, we need young people’s ideas and energy. College and university students anywhere in the world can download my book for free this week: https://gatesnot.es/2ZorCY0

This week, any college or university student anywhere in the world can download my book How to Avoid a Climate Disaster for free: https://gatesnot.es/3b5bltL
